OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy evening, with a few splashes of
OL,7,Flight rain or drizzle. Some evening
OL,8,Fglimmers of sunshine, mainly in the
OL,9,Feast. Murky overnight, with coastal
OL,10,Fmist and fog. Turning breezy in the
OL,11,Ffar west towards dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FRather cloudy in the west but
OL,14,Fturning much sunnier in the east.
OL,15,FFeeling very warm in the sunshine
OL,16,Fhere. Heavy rain and brisk winds in
OL,17,Fthe far west by evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
